body: Yes, fair enough. This fixes an internal issue, but one that's not critical or common. Best to do the right thing.

I'd like to revisit this PR. I keep seeing this known flake happen over and over, and the right fix, while almost ready, is still WIP. 

This PR's changes aren't that significant that reverting them will be too hard once the best solution is available.
